    Page: 462
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Surrrender
---
Surrender refreshes and regenerates. Failure to surrender strains and
wearies. Behind every genuine surrender lives a faith fulfilled; behind
every failure to surrender lies confidence betrayed.
